{"tid":1632842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支共出盡奶力打國際輿論戰","createTime":"2019-10-06T23:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T16:40:47.000Z","uid":289191,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ffdab11b5171d063d7b23b58602cecb69cf7d0","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:54:16.000Z","msg":"緊急法三天，支共的策略浮現了。<br />\n緊急法目的是刺激香港更亂，<br />\n安排黑警，紅的士，紅妓藝，<br />\n殺入人群製造衝突，<br />\n然後剪片＂FOCUS番＂示威者暴行，<br />\n加上火燒黨鐵黨銀等圖，<br />\nTWITTER 狂推。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bdb0d02996732d6eac56f32e1913ea39f99d97","tid":1632842,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:54:51.000Z","msg":"然後呢度啲人定唔知係咪打手我都分唔到繼續say文意完全係唔重要"},{"pid":"ec000dea9d34a65c9f355b074f640c38617e257f","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:56:56.000Z","msg":"支共主力在國際輿論，<br />\n在香港輿論就玩＂出口轉內銷＂。"},{"pid":"d2595ddce0d7de8c9dd39668d817dd85db22f8dd","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:05:39.000Z","msg":"之不過，衰在黑警又唔生性<br />\n搞喊小女孩，<br />\n又在街角圍DUP被捕者，<br />\n最核突果條片係：<br />\n黑警發現有人拍片立即舉盾摭住和停手。<br />\n一百果妖婦馬啼露<br />\n都唔及小女孩震撼。"},{"pid":"c0b4bd8c7c938af59f0a4d6f31122b8d4cc3c682","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2595ddce0d7de8c9dd39668d817dd85db22f8dd","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:05:39.000Z","msg":"之不過，衰在黑警又唔生性<br />\n搞喊小女孩，<br />\n又在街角圍DUP被捕者，<br />\n最核突果條片係：<br />\n黑警發現有人拍片立即舉盾摭住和停手。<br />\n一百果妖婦馬啼露<br />\n都唔及小女孩震撼。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:06:43.000Z","msg":"一百<del>果</del><span style=\"color: red;\">個</span>妖婦馬啼露<br />\n都唔及小女孩震撼。"},{"pid":"fc9509f05ad1b15029aebaf259c0429c00c842e8","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:16:37.000Z","msg":"支共的豬策略，<br />\n其實由六月十二至今一直無變，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打壓勇武者 + 宣傳分化和理非</span>。<br />\n四個月了，支共一輸再輸，<br />\n但係支共唔識收手，<br />\n只係越賭越大，<br />\n由香港城內賭到上國際。<br />\n支共係＂輸撚到懵咗＂(來自 Myradio《天地友政氣》姚冠東)"},{"pid":"1e87f7614c65d28f5235debbd165bc4839abd5d4","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:29:10.000Z","msg":"緊急法呢一鋪<br />\n可見支共已經＂輸撚到懵咗＂<br />\n支共以為國際社會<br />\n會＂FOCUS番＂黑衫打人放火<br />\n而忽視引用緊急法的本質和影響。<br />\n無計，支共的統治經驗，<br />\n只限於畜養十五億目光如豆的人形生物，<br />\n支共不知道<br />\n地球上大部份人有正常分析能力<br />\n可以分析事情因果本末和輕重。"},{"pid":"91e4ba557fc5e34de369bf3bc3bb3850f88cf5f3","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"緊急法，<br />\n是法治的相反詞。<br />\n如果香港法庭最終判政府勝訴<br />\n就連法治呢塊藥水膠布都搣甩埋<br />\n代表香港整個政治體制<br />\n完完全全是支共的工具"},{"pid":"d958e27490bbbe39061236fb3487967265d5b399","tid":1632842,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:57:29.000Z","msg":"睇過程，似係林奠故意挑引。<br />\n明知咁樣整個蒙面法出黎D人一定嬲到爆炸，然後夜晚武裝🐶故意俾你地破壞+搵臥底幫埋你破壞，然後約好晒出黎發表聲明繼續挑引班示威者。<br />\n佢D行為語氣，擺明挑機等你發爛。 <br />\n唔係錯判，似係中左佢正中下懷。"},{"pid":"14a6d877b17c9525aba9953d8eac6cca8721be0f","tid":1632842,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:59:35.000Z","msg":"唔一定要下下硬爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b885189f640ecf79ceca63aacfa4e0ad65164373","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:03:19.000Z","msg":"&quot; 正中下懷 &quot; 係你講嘅<br />\n我認為係支共中咗攬炒圈套"},{"pid":"b3563384655544de15843f4ff0b72c81c3a1f1d8","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:08:16.000Z","msg":"我的策略：<br />\n1) 推推推 黑警，紅的士惡行<br />\n2) 質疑馬蹄露，觀塘大火是否黑警所為"},{"pid":"56d8c62a937a53f2d3f9739dafee16fb1e1fe2e0","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2ffdab11b5171d063d7b23b58602cecb69cf7d0","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:54:16.000Z","msg":"緊急法三天，支共的策略浮現了。<br />\n緊急法目的是刺激香港更亂，<br />\n安排黑警，紅的士，紅妓藝，<br />\n殺入人群製造衝突，<br />\n然後剪片＂FOCUS番＂示威者暴行，<br />\n加上火燒黨鐵黨銀等圖，<br />\nTWITTER 狂推。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:17:47.000Z","msg":"安排黑警，紅的士，紅妓藝，<span style=\"color: red;\">持刀男</span> 殺入人群"},{"pid":"311a23d1787d3f08c1dcd52b0fc5611518bc6017","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:46:21.000Z","msg":"上TWITTER #HongKongProtests，<br />\n仲有兩段片：<br />\n1. 大陸白恤衫才俊被打<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChannelNewsAsia/status/1180835751853903873?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChannelNewsAsia%2Fstatus%2F1180835751853903873%3Fs%3D20&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=51f8ebdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChannelNewsAsia%2Fstatus%2F1180835751853903873%3Fs%3D20&h=7decfcc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ChannelNewsAsia/status/1180835751853903873?s=20</a><br />\n2. 背心電單車男清路障後被打 <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CarlZha/status/1180953022228131840?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCarlZha%2Fstatus%2F1180953022228131840%3Fs%3D20&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=b1ef9ade\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCarlZha%2Fstatus%2F1180953022228131840%3Fs%3D20&h=38adfaf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CarlZha/status/1180953022228131840?s=20</a><br />\n兩段都<span style=\"color: gold;\">好假</span>，<br />\n兩條友特登停步<span style=\"color: violet;\">好撚耐</span>，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">等人打</span><br />\n打手都係包到全身黑，健碩，打幾下即不知所踪。"},{"pid":"697ee41676a6be2949d4bf1ee47c3ab55897c9b8","tid":1632842,"uid":91218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b548e72026423737b32199f5c6f7e2383f6438b","tid":1632842,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:31:48.000Z","msg":"停裝修 人權法未過"},{"pid":"6f88a590de7f62619628dc2fc382a4189b18e62a","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"支共精心部署 Twitter 戰線<br />\n點知一單NBA火箭隊StandwithHongKong<br />\n就輸到嘔<br />\n奸有奸輸"},{"pid":"75d3ec4def42d44216f23971144bef2bdc24252b","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b548e72026423737b32199f5c6f7e2383f6438b","tid":1632842,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:31:48.000Z","msg":"停裝修 人權法未過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"傻喇<br />\n應做的事繼續做<br />\n你叫人兩個月停手<br />\n即係幫支共止暴制亂"},{"pid":"3d5a0eb445dd71846612836623e325b0a4dc9c10","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"支共的輿論宣傳戰<br />\n對香港人已無效<br />\n因為黑警卧底插贓嫁禍已是常識<br />\n輿論宣傳戰走上TWITTER<br />\n也有其弱點<br />\n1.    D片好假，無頭無尾<br />\n2.    D片中人樣衰，好難扮無辜<br />\n3.    Replies 水平也不及格，不難分辨出是 paid trolls."},{"pid":"22a92f7b9e8e7fff5f8b9ee4003c5d1c5bed3ef4","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"看看黑警官方TWITTER 如何卑鄙抹黑示威者:-----<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkpoliceforce/status/1181092514272464896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkpoliceforce%2Fstatus%2F1181092514272464896&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=48c95174\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkpoliceforce%2Fstatus%2F1181092514272464896&h=2a5a77d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkpoliceforce/status/1181092514272464896</a>"},{"pid":"a10af0b64fd54c608de648bac0d7b39071ba0e6c","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"NBA火箭事件，可能是天佑香港<br />\n支共精心怖置<br />\n要抹黑香港示威者的網上輿論大轟炸<br />\n無情情被火箭事件一筆勾消<br />\n香港絕對是得道者多助<br />\n支那網民把 Fight for Hong Kong 與 911 並列<br />\n美國人怒屌支那時<br />\n不禁想起香港人一再高舉Star spangled banner<br />\n火箭事件<br />\n可能是香港走出支那的觸發點"},{"pid":"b390330ed60417348ef4f5a686b4f31ae647a0dd","tid":1632842,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"睇睇呢條tweet: JPMorgan 中國男疑似被打<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Rozncrantz/status/1181478445567471616?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRozncrantz%2Fstatus%2F1181478445567471616%3Fs%3D20&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=0f1ac16c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRozncrantz%2Fstatus%2F1181478445567471616%3Fs%3D20&h=c98294ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Rozncrantz/status/1181478445567471616?s=20</a>"}]}